The PingDirectory App for Splunk gathers and presents throughput, latency, and GC metrics from PingDirectory via a series of customized reports and graphical illustrations.

This app supports PingDirectory version 8.0 and later.

See https://docs.pingidentity.com/pingdirectory/latest/pingdirectory_server_administration_guide/pd_ds_send_pd_metrics_statsd.html for instructions on configuring PingDirectory for use with the app.